import basicState from '../assets/icons8-full-image-96.png'
import checkState from '../assets/icons8-rectangle-96-green.png'
import Edit from '../assets/icons8-edit-96.png'
import Delete from '../assets/icons8-trash-96.png'
import Review from '../assets/writing.png'
import Add from '../assets/outline_add_black_18.png'
import Setting from '../assets/outline_settings_black_18.png'
import Search from '../assets/outline_search_black_18.png'

export const images = {
    uncompleted: basicState,
    completed: checkState,
    update: Edit,
    delete: Delete,
    deleteAll: Delete,
    review : Review,
    add : Add,
    setting : Setting,
    search : Search,
};
